.TH "nvme_init_get_log_reachability_associations" 9 "nvme_init_get_log_reachability_associations" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_log_reachability_associations \- Initialize passthru command for Reachability Associations Log
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_log_reachability_associations
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "bool rao "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_reachability_associations_log *log "  ","
.BI "__u32 len "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "rao" 12
Return associations only
.IP "log" 12
User address to store the log page
.IP "len" 12
The allocated length of the log page
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Log command with
LID value NVME_LOG_LID_REACHABILITY_ASSOCIATIONS
